snippet.title: Amber and Dolly: 9 to 5
snippet.description: Denbigh girl Amber Davies achieves her dreams of West End stardom in the hotly anticipated stage show  following Amber as she heads to Nashville to meet Dolly Parton herself, and sets about preparing for the biggest moment of her life. Having trained in musical theatre before embarking upon her Love Island journey, Amber is going back to her first love, to rekindle her passion for the stage, working ‘9 to 5’ to make her big dream come to fruition.
